msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn96:14.8"
msgid "sabbepi hi, bho gotama, cattāro vaṇṇā pahonti asmiṃ padese averaṃ abyābajjhaṃ mettacittaṃ bhāvetun”ti. "
msgstr "For all four classes are capable of developing a heart of love free of enmity and ill will for this region.” "

