msgstr "or workers goes forth from the lay life to homelessness. Relying on the teaching and training proclaimed by the Realized One … they succeed in the procedure of the skillful teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya16, sc16
msgctxt "mn96:16.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, brāhmaṇa, "
msgstr "What do you think, brahmin? "

msgctxt "mn96:16.2"
msgid "idha rājā khattiyo muddhāvasitto nānājaccānaṃ purisānaṃ purisasataṃ sannipāteyya: "
msgstr "Suppose an anointed aristocratic king were to gather a hundred people born in different castes and say to them: "

msgctxt "mn96:16.3"
msgid "‘āyantu bhonto ye tattha khattiyakulā brāhmaṇakulā rājaññakulā uppannā sākassa vā sālassa vā salaḷassa vā candanassa vā padumakassa vā uttarāraṇiṃ ādāya aggiṃ abhinibbattentu, tejo pātukarontu; "
msgstr "‘Please gentlemen, let anyone here who was born in a family of aristocrats, brahmins, or chieftains take a drill-stick made of teak, sal, frankincense wood, sandalwood, or cherry wood, light a fire and produce heat. "

msgctxt "mn96:16.4"
msgid "āyantu pana bhonto ye tattha caṇḍālakulā nesādakulā venakulā rathakārakulā pukkusakulā uppannā sāpānadoṇiyā vā sūkaradoṇiyā vā rajakadoṇiyā vā eraṇḍakaṭṭhassa vā uttarāraṇiṃ ādāya aggiṃ abhinibbattentu, tejo pātukarontū’”ti? "
msgstr "And let anyone here who was born in a family of outcastes, hunters, bamboo-workers, chariot-makers, or waste-collectors take a drill-stick made from a dog’s drinking trough, a pig’s trough, a dustbin, or castor-oil wood, light a fire and produce heat.’ "

# NOTE: start quotes in MS incorrect
#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.184, sc17
msgctxt "mn96:16.5"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, brāhmaṇa, "
msgstr "What do you think, brahmin? "

msgctxt "mn96:16.6"
msgid "yo evaṃ nu kho so khattiyakulā brāhmaṇakulā rājaññakulā uppannehi sākassa vā sālassa vā salaḷassa vā candanassa vā padumakassa vā uttarāraṇiṃ ādāya aggi abhinibbatto tejo pātukato so eva nu khvāssa aggi accimā ceva vaṇṇavā ca pabhassaro ca tena ca sakkā agginā aggikaraṇīyaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "Would only the fire produced by the high class people with good quality wood have flames, color, and radiance, and be usable as fire, "

msgctxt "mn96:16.7"
msgid "yo pana so caṇḍālakulā nesādakulā venakulā rathakārakulā pukkusakulā uppannehi sāpānadoṇiyā vā sūkaradoṇiyā vā rajakadoṇiyā vā eraṇḍakaṭṭhassa vā uttarāraṇiṃ ādāya aggi abhinibbatto tejo pātukato svāssa aggi na ceva accimā na ca vaṇṇavā na ca pabhassaro na ca tena sakkā agginā aggikaraṇīyaṃ kātun”ti? "
msgstr "and not the fire produced by the low class people with poor quality wood?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn96:16.8"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, bho gotama. "
msgstr "“No, Master Gotama. "

msgctxt "mn96:16.9"
msgid "Yopi hi so, bho gotama, khattiyakulā brāhmaṇakulā rājaññakulā uppannehi sākassa vā sālassa vā salaḷassa vā candanassa vā padumakassa vā uttarāraṇiṃ ādāya aggi abhinibbatto tejo pātukato svāssa aggi accimā ceva vaṇṇavā ca pabhassaro ca tena ca sakkā agginā aggikaraṇīyaṃ kātuṃ; "
msgstr "The fire produced by the high class people with good quality wood would have flames, color, and radiance, and be usable as fire, "

msgctxt "mn96:16.10"
msgid "yopi so caṇḍālakulā nesādakulā venakulā rathakārakulā pukkusakulā uppannehi sāpānadoṇiyā vā sūkaradoṇiyā vā rajakadoṇiyā vā eraṇḍakaṭṭhassa vā uttarāraṇiṃ ādāya aggi abhinibbatto tejo pātukato svāssa aggi accimā ceva vaṇṇavā ca pabhassaro ca tena ca sakkā agginā aggikaraṇīyaṃ kātuṃ. "
msgstr "and so would the fire produced by the low class people with poor quality wood. "

msgctxt "mn96:16.11"
msgid "Sabbopi hi, bho gotama, aggi accimā ceva vaṇṇavā ca pabhassaro ca sabbenapi sakkā agginā aggikaraṇīyaṃ kātun”ti. "
msgstr "For all fire has flames, color, and radiance, and is usable as fire.” "

